title: QNX RTOS SDP 6.4.0 Neutrino
description:
The QNX Software Development Platform 6.4.0 includes the QNX Neutrino RTOS 6.4.0 and QNX Momentics Tool Suite 6.4.0. It is a complete and comprehensive development environment for QNX Neutrino-based devices and systems. This DVD contains installers for Windows, Linux, and Neutrino-hosted installations.
